{"tid":1988980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有5日 五一黃金週我黎啦啦啦啦","createTime":"2020-04-25T14:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T14:45:20.000Z","uid":198418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7624f59f739051f94c8cd84604a1c7fdd80e195b","tid":1988980,"uid":198418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"好期待凸s呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxUF7a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxUF7a5.jpg&h=674ff83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃大綱&mdash;騎劫✋☝️黃金週<br />\n<br />\n活動另外一個部份係騎劫✋☝️黃金週<br />\n<br />\n當大家諗起五一黃金週，我相信，大家都會諗起中国人嘅五一黃金週假期🤢🤢，每一年五一黃金週都會有大量中国人入侵香港。<br />\n<br />\n所以，係今年，我地要去騎劫五一黃金週 將佢變成✋☝️黃金週，等人一見到✋☝️黃金週，就會諗起 五大訴求 缺一不可!<br />\n<br />\n而呢個計劃會有三個戰場，分別係本地戰線，外國戰線，以及牆內戰線。<br />\n<br />\n首先，喺本地戰線，文宣手足可以大量設計✋☝️黃金週文宣，嘗試以量取勝 。另外，手足們亦應多加善用文宣手足的設計，將這些設計大量傳送出去，例如whatsapp給所有contact，瘋狂air drop給路人。另外，希望大家能主動列印文宣，貼在不同地方，務求令香港人一見到✋☝️黃金周，就會聯想起五大訴求 缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n至於國際戰線，主平台將會是twitter，Reddit等平台。希望大家能在這些平台發佈和retweet✋☝️黃金周的文宣，並向世界宣傳什麼是 5 demands Not 1 less。再者，宜家twitter戰線係 #nnevvy 事件下，我地香港人同泰國人台灣人都統一陣線。我們希望能以 #5DN1L #5DemandsNot1Less 等hashtags (只是初步建議)，令更多人關注香港局勢。<br />\n<br />\n而牆內戰線。因為✋☝️在中国是極度敏感的，好似之前余文樂喺自家品牌度出現✋☝️手勢，已經激發一眾中国人嘅玻璃心。我覺得我地可以多加利用呢方面，瘋狂將五一黃金週和✋☝️黃金周、五大訴求 缺一不可、5 demands Not 1 less等字眼連上關係。令五一黃金週在中国變成禁語。<br />\n<br />\n主辦平台(排名不分先後):<br />\n<br />\n🖐☝️黃金週活動Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKGoldenWeek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKGoldenWeek&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=ed068aa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKGoldenWeek</a><br />\n<br />\n香城online<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/GloryHKGOnline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGloryHKGOnline&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=a88f8baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/GloryHKGOnline</a><br />\n<br />\n終極黃藍地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yellowshoppromotion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyellowshoppromotion&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=707512b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yellowshoppromotion</a><br />\n<br />\n民間記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=7e12c2f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\n<br />\n香港良心guide<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkshoplist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkshoplist&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=cfec04eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkshoplist</a>"},{"pid":"1df7184c82eb9b8e2452b9248d468fbdf11c212e","tid":1988980,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:45:11.000Z","msg":"Click<br />\nLike<br />\nShare(Subscribe埋呀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zbuRXqPI4l0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzbuRXqPI4l0&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=38e645bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zbuRXqPI4l0</a>"},{"pid":"0215f84caca20b751c3b5f8347aed9b3f4ca1734","tid":1988980,"uid":198418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"期待期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時大買特買"}]}